re du Loup]]\n** [[Kempt River]]\n*** [[East Kempt River]]\n**** [[North Kempt River]]\n*** [[West Kempt River]]\n** [[Matap\u00e9dia River]]\n*** [[Assemetquagan River]]\n**** [[East Assemetquagan River]]\n**** [[West Assemetquagan River]]\n*** [[Causapscal River]]\n**** [[South Causapscal River]]\n*** [[Sableuse River]]\n**** [[Inconnue River (Sableuse River tributary)|Inconnue River]]\n*** [[Sayabec River]]\n*** [[Saint-Pierre River (Matap\u00e9dia River tributary)|Saint-Pierre River]]\n**** [[Melucq River]]\n*** [[Tob\u00e9gote River]]\n*** [[Humqui River]]\n*** [[Matalik River]]\n*** [[Milnikek River]]\n**** [[Grande Rivi\u00e8re Milnikek Nord]]\n**** [[Vaseuse Rivere]]\n*** [[Rivi\u00e8re du Moulin (Matap\u00e9dia River tributary)|Rivi\u00e8re du Moulin]]\n** [[Patap\u00e9dia River]]\n*** [[Meadow River]]\n*** [[East Patap\u00e9dia River]]\n}}\n\n=== Restigouche River watershed (part in New Brunswick) ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n'''Right bank'''\n*[[Upsalquitch River]]\n**[[Popelogan River]]\n**[[Southeast Upsalquitch River]]\n***[[Little Southeast Upsalquitch River]]\n**[[Northwest Upsalquitch River]]\n*[[Little Main Restigouche River]]\n**[[Gounamitz River]]\n***[[North Branch Gounamitz River]]\n***[[West Branch Gounamitz River]]\n\n'''Left bank'''\n*[[Kedgwick River]]\n**[[Belle Kedgwick River]]\n**[[South Branch Kedgwick River]]\n}}\n\n== Watershed of Bay of Fundy (Atlantic Ocean) ==\n\n===Saint John River watershed \u2013 higher part (Quebec, Maine and New Brunswick)===\n\n'''North bank of [[Saint John River (Bay of Fundy)|Saint John River]]'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Southwest Branch Saint John River]], Quebec and [[Maine]]\n* [[Northwest Branch Saint John River]], Maine\n** [[Daaquam River]], Quebec and Maine\n*** [[Roche River (Daaquam River tributary)|Roche River]], Quebec\n**** [[Onze River]], Quebec\n**** [[Douze River]], Quebec\n*** [[Black River (Daaquam River tributary)|Black River]], Quebec\n**** [[Little River (Black River t